ActElectoral Boundaries Readjustment Act
SubjectOrder Designating the Minister of Public Safety and Emergency Preparedness as the Minister for the Purposes of the Electoral Boundaries Readjustment Act
PrecisOrder (1) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2021-942 of October 26, 2021; and (2) designating the Minister of PUBLIC SAFETY AND EMERGENCY PREPAREDNESS, a member of the King’s Privy Council for Canada, as the Minister for the purposes of the ELECTORAL BOUNDARIES READJUSTMENT ACT.
